/**
 * Title       : activity_search_results order
 * Purpose     : Show results of the search

 * Date        : 15.10.2016
 * Input       : String query

 * Proccessing : Get data from DB related to query and show it in the ListView
 *
 * Output      : Activity
 *
 * @author Mikhail PASTUSHKOV
